<section class="page-section">
  <h2>What this workbook is for</h2>
  <p>
    This workbook focuses on the first level of the Quiet Power system:
    control starts with what you let in, what you ignore, and what you choose to delay.
  </p>
  <p>
    It helps you see that before you can control your actions, you need to control your inputs —
    the signals, noise, and hits from the world that you allow to land.
  </p>
</section>
